# Set default behavior for all files to normalize line endings to LF.
# This is the standard for Go and cross-platform projects.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly handle file types to ensure consistency.
# Go files
*.go text
go.mod text
go.sum text

# Web and template files
*.js text
*.css text
*.html text
*.tmpl text

# Config and docs
*.yaml text
*.md text